reviewText: I really liked the movie. I think that it was really cute and all of the stuff that happened on the golf course was really funny. The quality of the film is great. It plays really well. I am very satisfied.
I used to watch popples when i was little. This video was so inexpensive so i had to get it and it was in perfect condition. my 4 year old daughter loves it!
The complete series of the Popples is coming out in the UK in a month or two as well as Rainbow brite complete. Of course that's region 2 PAL though!
I wish to see them on T.V. again. I find them clean and no fighting and no hurting no one. Everyone loves everyone. Please let me when there any for sale, I will good.
